Python project using fastapi.

### Conventions
- Follow PEP 8; use type hints on public functions.
- Run the tests with pytest before finishing a task.
- Do not introduce new dependencies without adding them to the existing dependency manifest.

### Architecture
- Keep business logic separate from the framework layer when the project already follows that pattern.
- Use virtual environments; never install packages globally.

