- Keep components/modules small and single-purpose.
- Place tests next to the code they cover or in a mirrored \`test/\` directory, following what the repo already uses.

## Canonical commands

- test: \`npm test\` (package.json)
- lint: \`npm run lint\` (package.json)

## Repo commands

- \`npm test\` → \`mocha --recursive test/\` (package.json)
- \`npm run lint\` → \`eslint lib/ test/\` (package.json)

